    <item>
      <title>随着全球套利交易平仓增加，日元延续涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/yen-extends-advance-as-global-carry-trade-unwind-ramps-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日元兑美元周三突破关键水平，引领全球套利交易平仓，导致墨西哥比索、澳元和新西兰元等多种货币下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/yen-extends-advance-as-global-carry-trade-unwind-ramps-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 05:04:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>桑坦德银行提高收入目标，博廷银行效率提高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/santander-posts-record-profit-as-it-beat-quarterly-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[桑坦德银行上调了今年的收入增长目标，并表示在第二季度创下创纪录的利润后，将继续致力于控制成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/santander-posts-record-profit-as-it-beat-quarterly-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 05:02:56 GMT</pubDate>
